# Keep the best weights of EVERY run in model/runs/ in the repo, so a fresh
# clone has all our trained models ready and the prof never has to retrain.
# Glob covers current and future runs automatically (last.pt stays ignored).
!model/runs/*/weights/best.pt
data/**/*.cache

